definitions.definition: A town and civil parish with a town council in West Devon district, Devon , England ( OS grid ref SX4874 ) .
A community , formerly a village, in East Zorra-Tavistock township, Ontario , Canada .
An unincorporated community in New Castle County , Delaware , United States .
A minor borough in Camden County , New Jersey , United States .
